! DEC   Solar declination or (90o - solar elevation at noon) (deg.)
! DOY   Day of year (d)
! PI    PI=3.14159 (rad)
! RAD   RAD=PI/180. (rad./deg.)
! SNDN  Time of sunset (hr)
